Name: LP
Description: Executing LP - counterparty to the trade.

Name: OutCome
Description: If the trade was WON or LOST.

Name: Symbol
Description: Currency pair. For example EURUSD.

Name: Side
Description: Trade side. "B” for buy and "S” for sell.

Name: NearTradeQuantity
Description: Neg leg traded quantity expressed in TradeCurrency

Name: FarTradeQuantity
Description: Far leg traded quantity expressed in TradeCurrency

Name: TradeCcy
Description:
Denomination Currency for TradeQuantity and OrderQuantity. For example
    EUR.

Name: TradeTime
Description: TradeTime - Time (GMT) when the trade was filled

Name: FarPrice
Description: Price of the far leg quoted

Name: NearPrice
Description: Price of the near leg quoted

Name: NearForwardPoints
Description: Near leg forward point quoted

Name: FarForwardPoints
Description: Far leg forward point quoted

Name: NearPriceShown
Description: Price the near leg traded at

Name: FarPriceShown
Description: Price the far leg traded at

Name: NearFPShown
Description: Near leg forward point traded

Name: FarFPShown
Description: Far leg forward point traded

Name: ProductType
Description: Type of product traded. For example SPOT

Name: ShownFP
Description: The forward point that was shown

Name: WinningFP
Description: The winning forward point

Name: MissedFP
Description: Difference between the WinningFP and ShownFP
